data.description: Assumable VA 2.75%! You will be seduced by the charms of this beautifully updated home in Vista Ridge. A welcoming ambiance combined with a friendly neighborhood will make you feel excited to come home each day. There's ample space for entertaining and relaxation in the oversized living room that opens into both the kitchen and the dining room. Suffer from allergies? Updated engineered hardwood flooring and tile in the wet areas span throughout the home; no carpet. The sleek kitchen has been kitted out with plenty of storage and countertop space, allowing you to easily prep and serve meals. The lovely dining room flows to the sun-lit deck, which serves as an ideal spot for some R & R. The spacious owner's suite is a warm, intimate space, conducive to quiet reading or a peaceful night of sleep. Pamper yourself in the ensuite bath with an oversized, dual vanity, soaking tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. Head upstairs to a spacious flex area that features the most incredible views. The 3 guest bedrooms on the 2nd floor are all a great size. Accomplish all of your tasks and more in the dedicated front office while you are working from home. A designated dining zone flows through to the expansive back deck, where families can gather for meals, play and enjoy unobstructed greenbelt views. An already established garden is prepped and ready for your favorite vegetables to be planted. The resort-style community amenities provide an abundance of fun for the entire family and include a pool, park and playground. This residential community is a comfortable, peaceful haven, yet perfectly situated to take advantage of all the city has to offer. This special property could be your forever home, come see it today!
